 <text id="F3071T">
  <front id="d2">
   <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
    <p>Demus expresses disappointment that Mary Jane has not written recently and urges her to write
     again.</p>
   </div1>
  </front>

  <body id="d4">
   <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
    <head>
     <name type="recipient">Mary Jane Demus</name>
    </head>

    <opener>
     <dateline>
      <date value="1863-10-15"><orig reg="writing">riton</orig> the 15th of october</date>
      <name type="place">
       <orig reg="Morris">Mor</orig>
       <orig reg="island">ilon</orig>
       <orig reg="South Carolina">SCarlia</orig>
      </name>
     </dateline>
     <salute><orig reg="My">Mi</orig> Dear</salute>
    </opener>

    <p>i <orig reg="must">mus</orig> set down this <orig reg="morning">morn</orig> and tell you What
     i think <orig reg="about">a boute</orig> you <orig reg="for">fer</orig> i <orig reg="know">now</orig>
     <orig reg="very">verry</orig> Well that if you <orig reg="thought">thot</orig> as much of me as
     i <orig reg="do">dou</orig> of you <orig reg="Why">Wiy</orig> you <orig reg="Would">Wod</orig>
     <orig reg="write">righte</orig> more then <orig reg="What">Whot</orig> you <orig reg="do">dou</orig>
     <orig reg="for">fer</orig> i have <orig reg="wrote">rote</orig>
     <orig reg="four">fore</orig> letter and <orig reg="haven't">hant</orig> got one yet and i <orig
      reg="Would">Wod</orig> like to <orig reg="know">now</orig> What is the
     <unclear>reachen</unclear> that you <orig reg="don't">doan</orig>
     <orig reg="write">righte</orig> more then What you do and let me <orig reg="know">now</orig>
     how you <orig reg="are">ar</orig>
     <orig reg="for">fer</orig>
     <unclear>thar</unclear> is all the <orig reg="rest">reste</orig> of the boys <orig
      reg="getting">geting</orig> letter <orig reg="every">evr</orig> time that the <orig reg="mail"
      >male</orig>
     <orig reg="Come">Cum</orig> in but if you <orig reg="ain't">ant</orig> Able to <orig
      reg="write">righte</orig>
     <orig reg="Why">Wiy</orig> i <orig reg="shall">shal</orig> not think <orig reg="hard">harde</orig>
     <orig reg="about">a boute</orig>
     <orig reg="it">i</orig> but if you <orig reg="are">ar</orig> Well and <orig reg="don't">doant</orig>
     <orig reg="write">righte</orig>
     <orig reg="Why">Wiy</orig> i <orig reg="shall">shal</orig> give <orig reg="up">oup</orig> too
     if you had much <orig reg="feeling">fealing</orig>
     <orig reg="for">fer</orig> me <orig reg="Why">Wiy</orig> you <orig reg="Would">Wod</orig>
     <orig reg="write">right</orig> to me <orig reg="for">fer</orig> i <orig reg="Can't">Cant</orig>
     get paper <orig reg="only">oneley</orig>
     <orig reg="sometimes">som times</orig> but i hope that you Will <orig reg="please">pleas</orig>
     to <orig reg="write">righte</orig>
     <orig reg="Once">Wons</orig> more and let me <orig reg="know">now</orig> how you <orig
      reg="are">ar</orig> and all the <orig reg="rest">reste</orig>
     <orig reg="please">pleas</orig> to give <orig reg="my">mi</orig> love to all the <orig
      reg="friends">frends</orig> i hope that you Will <unclear>Cape</unclear> this letter for to
     look at <orig reg="for">fer</orig> i am <orig reg="getting">geting</orig>
     <orig reg="along">a long</orig>
     <orig reg="very">verrey</orig> Well at this time i am <orig reg="Waiting">Waying</orig> on
      <orig reg="officer">offerser</orig> and i have <unclear>now</unclear>
     <orig reg="hard">harde</orig>
     <unclear>think</unclear> to <orig reg="Do">Dow</orig></p>

    <p><orig reg="Direct">Directe</orig>
     <orig reg="your">yor</orig> letter to morris <orig reg="island">ilon</orig> SC<lb/> 54 <orig
      reg="massachusetts">mastues</orig><lb/>
     <abbr expan="Colored">Col</abbr>
     <orig reg="regiment">redment</orig><lb/>
     <orig reg="Company">Comey</orig><lb/> to</p>

    <closer>
     <salute><orig reg="your">yor</orig> Dear <orig reg="friend">frend</orig></salute>
     <signed>David <orig reg="Demus">Dimes</orig></signed>
    </closer>
   </div1>
  </body>
